name: STRESS.
description:
A fast-paced endless runner about a student who goes bonkers.

F / Space to Jump

D / Shift to Duck

J to Throw

TAB - Main Menu

ENTER - Restart

Painting Art by Tanjerine - https://www.instagram.com/tanjereine/

Music by TheMidiMan - https://twitter.com/TheMIDIMan1

Everything Else by iamcheeze - https://iamcheeze.itch.io/

If the UI elements aren't in the black bars, try downloading it, then readjust the window.
